author: Zoe Shenton
title: Bianca Gascoigne blasts ex CJ Meeks for 'paying girls to pose with him for staged pap shots'
text:
Bianca Gascoigne blasts ex CJ Meeks for 'paying girls to pose with him for staged pap shots' Cagefighter CJ was pictured snogging an Irish glamour model on Valentine's Day Share Bianca has a dig at her ex (Photo: Barcroft) Share Get celebs   Thank you for subscribing!   
Bianca Gascoigne has blasted her ex CJ Meeks on Instagram, accusing him of paying a model to pose with him for a set up paparazzi photoshoot. 
On Tuesday night, CJ was pictured in London kissing and cuddling up to a blonde bombshell called Shannen. 
Bianca's ex and the Irish glamour model attended a Valentine’s Day boat party before partying at DSTRKT nightclub and looked totally smitten with one another. 
However, on Wednesday night, the Celebrity Big Brother star took to Instagram to share a screengrab of a Facebook post that appeared to be written by the model he spent the evening with. 
"I was asked to go on a set up date lol nothing in it it was all staged just to let everyone know 100 per cent staged (sic)," she wrote. Bianca Gascoigne (Photo: Lia Toby/WENN.com) 
Alongside the screengrab, Bianca fumed: "Wow my ex is seriously going to lengths now paying girls to go on dates with him so he can do set up pap shots to get in the papers online!" Read More Bianca Gascoigne's ex CJ Meeks SLAMS her after Jamie O'Hara split: "It's karma" 
Last week, CJ was spotted moving out of his home with Bianca after she kissed and flirted with Jamie O'Hara on Celebrity Big Brother . 
CJ and Bianca had been living together for five months before she went into the house, but the glamour model claimed during her exit interview that they weren't a proper couple. 
The cagefighter disagreed, saying all he had done was tell the truth and said he believes Bianca was just chasing fame. Bianca Gascoigne and her cage fighter boyfriend C.J. Meeks seen at Bluebird Garage restaurant on July 24, 2016 in London (Photo: Barcroft Media) Read More CJ Meeks spotted snogging Bianca Gascoigne lookalike on romantic date night after ex’s split from Jamie O’Hara 
"I did not want any of this, she wanted to see if she could go and get famous and unfortunately she has got famous for all the wrong reasons," he told The Sun . 
It comes after Jamie, 30, told Rinse FM that while Bianca is a "wicked girl", he has too much in his life to make room for a relationship with her. 
"I think at the moment we'll just stay friends, we're going to hang out," he admitted. (Photo: Eagle Lee / Barcroft Media) Jamie O'Hara 'Lorraine' TV show (Photo: Rex Features) Read More Jamie O'Hara comes clean about Bianca Gascoigne dumping: 'I've got loads going on' 
"I had a wicked time in house but I've got loads on in my personal life. I've got my kids, I've got lots of work coming up. We're just going to be friends." 
But it was the first Bianca had heard that Jamie wanted to remain single - just days before he was calling her "wifey material" and saying she could be The One . Video Loading Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now
